These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-1::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, chaman, cain, alhambra, game
There are 5 different favourite colors: brown, apricot, ivory, green, ebony
1. the person who likes apricot is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes brown is somewhere between the person who likes ebony and the alhambra-smoker##7
3. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who likes green is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ivory##5
6. the person who likes ebony is somewhere between the chaman-smoker and the cain-smoker##7
7. the person who likes green is somewhere to the right of the alhambra-smoker##5
8. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the right of the person who likes brown##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |        2        |      3       |     4      |      5      |
| Cigar           | alhambra | cain | game | chaman | bluemaster    |
| Color   | apricot      | brown          | ebony   | green     | ivory |

