.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-2::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: rock, jazz, ambient, r&b, electronic
5 different pets are kept: goat, lizard, goldfish, dog, frog
1. the fan ambient is somewhere to the left of the fan r&b##5
2. the fan electronic is between the fan jazz and the owner of the dog##2
3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
5. the fan jazz is somewhere to the left of the fan electronic##5
6. the owner of the goat is on the far left or far right##3
7. the fan electronic is somewhere between the fan r&b and the owner of the lizard##7
8. the fan rock is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |   3    |     4     |   5   |
| Music-Genre        | rock | jazz | electronic | ambient | r&b  |
| Pet   | goat   | lizard   | goldfish | dog     | frog |

