.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-3::.
5 different games are played: whist, billiard, snooker, go, scrabble
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: november, august, december, february, may
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person playing whist##1
2. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5
3. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in february##7
4. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##5
5. the person playing whist is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
7. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |     4     |    5    |
| Game          | snooker  | scrabble   | go | billiard      | whist |
| Birthday   | august | december | november   | february | may  |

