.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: singing, gardening, baking, card-games, sudoku
There 5 different types of food: orange, pineapple, grapes, apple, eggplant
1. the person eating grapes is somewhere between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is card-games##7
2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far right##1
3. the person eating pineapple is somewhere between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's hobby is card-games##7
4. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
6. the person eating orange is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person eating orange##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |    5     |
| Hobby   | singing | card-games | baking | sudoku    | gardening |
| Food     | eggplant     | apple     | grapes | pineapple | orange     |

