.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-6::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: mirinda, fanta, soy-milk, cola, juice
House: ranch-style, cape-cod, townhouse, art-deco, futuristic
1. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the ranch-style house and the person drinking fanta##7
2. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the ranch-style house##5
3. the art-deco house is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
4. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere between the art-deco house and the person drinking juice##7
5. the cape-cod house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere between the cape-cod house and the person drinking fanta##7
7. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
8. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
9. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |    3    |     4     |      5       |
| Beverage   | juice | mirinda | soy-milk  | cola | fanta |
| House           | ranch-style    | cape-cod  | townhouse | art-deco    | futuristic        |

