 1. the person traveling to boston is not the victorian house##6
 2. the gothic-revival house is somewhere between the person traveling to new-york and the person traveling to boston##7
 3. the victorian house is on the far left##1
 4. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the cottage house##1
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 6. the cape-cod house is the person traveling to new-york##1
 7. the person traveling to boston is the cottage house##1
 8. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
 9. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the cottage house##1
10. the cottage house is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
11. the person traveling to liverpool is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |   2   |       3       |      4      |   5    |
| House   | victorian | craftsman | cape-cod | gothic-revival | cottage  |
| City        | liverpool     | prague   | new-york          | hannover    | boston |

