3. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
4. the person watching sports movies is somewhere between the person who growszinnia and the person watching spy movies##7
5. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
6. the person watching satire movies is not the person who growsdahlia##6
7. the person who growsdahlia is the person watching spy movies##1
8. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1
9. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
