There are 5 different nationalities: spanish, thai, british, pakistani, mexican
The people have 5 different hobbies: puzzles, chess, collecting, rock-climbing, drawing
 1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 2. the thai is not the person who's hobby is drawing##6
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the spanish##1
 5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
 6. the thai is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 7. the thai is on the right of the mexican##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the mexican and the british##7
 9. the person who's hobby is chess is not the british##6
10. the mexican is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |      2      |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Nationality   | mexican | thai | pakistani | british     | spanish       |
| Hobby      | rock-climbing   | chess    | collecting | drawing | puzzles |

