 1. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is the person playing go##1
 3. the person playing poker is in an odd position##4
 4. the person playing backgammon is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is not the person playing poker##6
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere between the person playing poker and the person who's birthday is in may##7
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 8. the person playing backgammon is not the person who's birthday is in september##6
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5
10. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
11. the person playing snooker is not the person who's birthday is in september##6
12. the person playing snooker is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
13. the person who's birthday is in january is the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |   2   |   3    |   4    |    5    |
